OL,7,GUK broadcasting regulator Ofcom says
OL,8,Grules that limit the number of
OL,9,Gadverts on ITV 1, Channel 4 and
OL,10,GChannel 5 are no longer justified or
OL,11,Gproportionate.
OL,13,FRules limiting the number of adverts
OL,14,Fon what are now known as commercial
OL,15,Fpublic service channels were put in
OL,16,Fplace 30 years ago.
OL,18,FBack then, the difference was between
OL,19,Fcable and satellite services which
OL,20,Fhad greater freedom and two
OL,21,Fterrestrial channels carrying a
OL,22,Frestricted number of adverts.
OL,3,COfcom consults on increasing ad time
OL,4,Con ITV 1 and other public service
OL,5,Cchannels
