OL,7,FThe two terrestrial channels (your
OL,8,Flocal ITV station and either Channel
OL,9,F4 or S4C) could command greater fees
OL,10,Ffor ad time due to their vastly
OL,11,Flarger reach.
OL,13,FThree decades later and with every
OL,14,Fhousehold able to receive a variety
OL,15,Fof channels, Ofcom has indicated it's
OL,16,Ftime for change.
OL,18,FFollowing a call for evidence last
OL,19,Fyear, Ofcom has now launched a
OL,20,Fconsultation on two possible options:
OL,3,COfcom consults on increasing ad time
OL,4,Con ITV 1 and other public service
OL,5,Cchannels
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G2/4
